== 製作 ==
本劇由{{link-en|查德·賀智|Chad Hodge}}、[[奈特·沙馬蘭|奈特·沙馬蘭]]、{{link-en|唐納德·迪·賴恩|Donald De Line}}與艾希溫·拉傑恩擔任執行製作，試播集由查德·賀智撰寫、奈特·沙馬蘭執導。<ref name=midseason/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fox.com/wayward-pines/ |title=Wayward Pines |publisher=[[福斯廣播公司|Fox]] |accessdate=2014-03-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314103239/http://www.fox.com/wayward-pines/ |archivedate=2014-03-14 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/fox-greenlights-m-night-shyamalan-event-series-wayward-pines-matt-dillon-to-star/ |author=Andreeva, Nellie |title=Fox Greenlights M. Night Shyamalan Event Series ''Wayward Pines'', Matt Dillon To Star |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2013-05-13 |accessdate=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2013-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019124132/http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/fox-greenlights-m-night-shyamalan-event-series-wayward-pines-matt-dillon-to-star/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20775362_2,00.html |title=TV: 14 Shows That Should be on Your Radar (And Soon, Your DVR) (#5) |author=Vilkomerson, Sara |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2014-01-10 |accessdate=2015-05-18 |archive-date=2014-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141107134843/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20775362_2,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/01/09/m-knight-shyamalan-wayward-pines/ |work=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]] |author=Vilkomerson, Sara |title=M. Night Shyamalan's TV debut ''Wayward Pines'': A first look |date=2014-01-09 |accessdate=2016-03-05 |archive-date=2014-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141128134109/http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/01/09/m-knight-shyamalan-wayward-pines/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年5月13日，FOX正式預訂本系列10集。本劇在2013年8月19日至2014年2月14日間於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[不列顛哥倫比亞|不列顛哥倫比亞]]的[[本那比|本那比]]（棚內）、{{link-en|阿格西 (不列顛哥倫比亞)|Agassiz, British Columbia|阿格西}}（外景）拍攝。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://globalnews.ca/news/780328/stars-set-to-begin-work-on-wayward-pines-in-b-c/|publisher=全球新聞|author=John R. Kennedy|title=Stars set to begin work on ''Wayward Pines'' in B.C.|date=2014-08-14|accessdate=2015-05-18|archive-date=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714102130/http://globalnews.ca/news/780328/stars-set-to-begin-work-on-wayward-pines-in-b-c/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本劇改編自{{link-en|布萊克·克勞奇|Blake Crouch}}的系列小說《{{link-en|松林異境|The Wayward Pines Trilogy}}》，第一季前五集是根據2012年出版的第一部《迷途》（{{lang|en|Pines}}）改編，後五集劇情則是由2013年出版的第二部《淪陷》（{{lang|en|Wayward}}）與2014年出版的第三部《最後小鎮》（{{lang|en|The Last Town}}）改編集結而成。<ref name=pierce>{{cite news |first=Scott D. |last=Pierce |url=http://www.sltrib.com/entertainment/2489265-155/scott-d-pierce-no-theyre-not |title=No, they're not dead on ''Wayward Pines'' |work={{link-en|鹽湖城論壇報|The Salt Lake Tribune}} |date=2015-05-11 |accessdate=2015-06-13 |archive-date=2017-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619055727/http://www.sltrib.com/entertainment/2489265-155/scott-d-pierce-no-theyre-not |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010672762|title=博客來-松林異境三部曲【《陰松林》原著影集書衣版】|work=[[博客來|博客來]]]]|accessdate=2016-03-05|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305145940/http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010672762|dead-url=no}}</ref>奈特·沙馬蘭表示電視劇版和小說有些許差異，而在電視劇開發期間，克勞奇尚再撰寫小說。<ref name=pierce/>2015年6月，[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]表示FOX基於本劇獲得不錯的收視，有意製作第二季。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Andreeva|first1=Nellie|title='Wayward Pines' Hits Season High & Sets DVR Lift Record, Could Get 2nd Season|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/wayward-pines-high-dvr-lift-record-season-2-renewal-1201452683/|accessdate=2015-07-01|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-06-25|archive-date=2015-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629020111/http://deadline.com/2015/06/wayward-pines-high-dvr-lift-record-season-2-renewal-1201452683/|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而開創查德·賀智表示：「《陰松林》是設定為只有10集的電視劇。」使得製作第二季的可能性縮減。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2015/07/23/wayward-pines-finale-ethan-dies-time-jump/|title='Wayward Pines' Series Finale Recap — Ethan and Pilcher Die, Time Jump to 4031 - TVLine|author=Matt Webb Mitovich|work=TVLine|accessdate=2016-03-05|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193643/http://tvline.com/2015/07/23/wayward-pines-finale-ethan-dies-time-jump/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TVLine Post Mortem">{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2015/06/11/wayward-pines-episode-5-aberrations-year-4028/|title=''Wayward Pines'' Post Mortem — Abnormal Humans in Year 4028 - TVLine|author=Matt Webb Mitovich|work=TVLine|accessdate=2016-03-05|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305072513/http://tvline.com/2015/06/11/wayward-pines-episode-5-aberrations-year-4028/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他表示：「季終雖為開放式結局，但他會是故事的完結。」<ref name="TVLine Post Mortem"/>隨著季終的播出，顯示第一季第10集為“系列完結”，也正式為本劇畫下句點。<ref>{{cite web|author=Roco|title=''Wayward Pines'' Cancelled By FOX After One Season|url=http://seriable.com/wayward-pines-cancelled-by-fox-after-one-season/|publisher=Seriable|date=2015-07-17|accessdate=2015-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717161322/http://seriable.com/wayward-pines-cancelled-by-fox-after-one-season/|archive-date=2015-07-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>然而在2015年12月9日，FOX考慮到本劇收視不錯，故正式宣布續訂本劇第二季，並預計於2016年中旬首播。<ref name="Season2"/>

第2季起，在查德·賀智卸下主理人與執行製作的職位後，由馬克·弗里德曼接替其職位。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/12/m-night-shyamalan-wayward-pines-renewed-season-2-fox-new-showrunner-1201663497/|title=M. Night Shyamalan’s ‘Wayward Pines’ Renewed By Fox For Season 2 With New Showrunner|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|website=Deadline|access-date=2016-04-20|archive-date=2016-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503170643/http://deadline.com/2015/12/m-night-shyamalan-wayward-pines-renewed-season-2-fox-new-showrunner-1201663497/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

